{"tid":2060700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國財長：或限制美資本經香港流動 以回應港區國安法","createTime":"2020-06-12T00:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:30:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b657d52096ecfc3a78f1ec6269fb53a1a05982","tid":2060700,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國財長姆努欽稱，可能限制美國資本經香港流動，以回應中國在香港推出港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n姆努欽向傳媒表示，特朗普政府將透過總統的資本市場工作小組，負責探討中國在香港推行港區國安法美國作出的各種回應，小組正研究限制美國資本經香港流動的一些措施，而小組亦將會研究與中國企業相關的會計問題，並將發表一份全面的報告。<br />\n<br />\n面對中美關係緊張，姆努欽說，他仍然預料中國將履行中美第一階段貿易協議的條款，根據美國農業部最新數據，過去兩周，中國國有和私人買家積極採購美國大豆，美國過去兩周至少出口150萬噸大豆予中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394132&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0m6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=15046e37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394132&h=b4d5b6de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394132</a>"},{"pid":"dc0b4cfee0454e6303daecf752524a86d7238905","tid":2060700,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:19:17.000Z","msg":"或，可能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad4dae2f146e4824b7cad990e6aed6f01960311","tid":2060700,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488b5c5dcb24a47c198ae927476e8b8c5e4f6fee","tid":2060700,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"制裁左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等緊你呀"},{"pid":"82e7c470bf5365cf1cb037a8ad77